<Overview3Cols>
    <Text1>
        <strong>Bots</strong> enable remote Proxmox VE cluster management through Telegram chatbot integration.<br />
        Administrators can execute commands, monitor system status, and manage node operations directly from Telegram.<br />
        With support for command aliases and automated workflows, the chatbot enhances control and reduces manual intervention.<br />
    </Text1>

    <Text2>
        <strong>Remote Control</strong>: Execute commands and manage nodes through secure Telegram bot.<br />
        <strong>Real-time Alerts</strong>: Receive instant notifications for cluster events and status changes.<br />
        <strong>Secure Access</strong>: Token-based authentication ensures controlled bot access.<br />
    </Text2>

    <Text3>
        <strong>Mobile-First</strong>: Full cluster management from any device with Telegram app.<br />
        <strong>Instant Response</strong>: Get immediate feedback on commands and system status.<br />
        <strong>Simple Commands</strong>: Chat-based interface makes complex operations accessible.<br />
    </Text3>
</Overview3Cols>
